Date: Fri, 20 Sep 2019 18:35:30 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Fix asm option compatibility

To stay compatible with the Meson options from Mesa 19.0,
reintroduce a dummy "asm" option in meson_options.txt

---
 meson_options.txt | 6 ++++++
 1 file changed, 6 insertions(+)

diff --git a/meson_options.txt b/meson_options.txt
index 35786bf5caf..e9bebb729fe 100644
--- a/meson_options.txt
+++ b/meson_options.txt
@@ -241,6 +241,12 @@ option(
   value : false,
   description : 'Enable GLVND support.'
 )
+option(
+  'asm',
+  type : 'boolean',
+  value : true,
+  description : 'Build assembly code if possible'
+)
 option(
    'glx-read-only-text',
    type : 'boolean',
